  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then-- that's how I got my false papers and my sister too because he did it, and he did some for himself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he came to visit me every day to this hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you have to know that this time, when you enter this hospital, you had to show your papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was always put himself into a risk that somebody discover that the papers are false.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was-- went as far as went in to the-- the captain, the highest office in the hospital, and he said that I am in love with a Jewish girl who is-- who you are keeping in this hospital and I would like very much if you would let her go and just make an exception, because I want to marry her, no matter if she's Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But, of course, they didn't let me out and then she-- he decided, my husband, still not my husband, he decided that he's giving me the papers, telling me the address where my sister was already with the boy, and then-- my sister just told me after I was talking to you-- I was talking to her, and she told me that the house where-- where she went to live with the false papers, it was a house where a lot of Jewish people lived and they were taken away.",
      "word_count": 90
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you had to put in an application as a non-Jewish person whether you can occupy that flat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she wasn't by herself there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were a lot of others in the same flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was two or three bedrooms, and they couldn't afford to put everybody so they put a lot of them in the same flat.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
